title: Episode 40 - David Morris Interview (Brink Vault 2014)
itunes:title: Episode 40 - David Morris Interview (Brink Vault 2014)
description: Our final interview in our 'vault' series today as we travel back to 2014 for an extremely entertaining chat with Australia's surprise silver medalist from Sochi, aerial skier David Morris. From his expectations going into the games to just why he tried to trade his medal, this is one chat that you definitely will be smiling throughout it.
